<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f3ede5;
      --paper: rgba(255, 250, 244, 0.92);
      --text: #24170f;
      --muted: #6c584b;
      --accent: #b85d2f;
      --accent-soft: rgba(184, 93, 47, 0.12);
      --line: rgba(68, 46, 32, 0.12);
      --good: #2d7c54;
      --shadow: 0 28px 60px rgba(46, 29, 18, 0.12);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(248, 209, 178, 0.9), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(184, 93, 47, 0.12), transparent 24%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #faf5ef, var(--bg));
    }
    .page {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100vw - 28px));
      margin: 18px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .nav, .hero, .highlights, .footer-links { display: grid; gap: 18px; }
    .nav {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      align-items: center;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .brand { font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
    .nav-links, .cta-row, .footer-links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
    .nav-links a, .cta-row a, .footer-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .cta-row a.primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff8f3;
      border-color: transparent;
    }
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(280px, 0.7fr);
      align-items: stretch;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .panel {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fffaf5;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 0.92;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .subtitle {
      margin: 14px 0 0;
      max-width: 54ch;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(45, 124, 84, 0.12);
      color: var(--good);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45, 124, 84, 0.18);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }
    .status-card {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      align-content: start;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.92), rgba(248, 238, 228, 0.92));
    }
    .status-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent);
      width: fit-content;
    }
    .status-dot {
      width: 11px;
      height: 11px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--good);
    }
    .metrics {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .metric {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .metric strong { display: block; font-size: 1.7rem; margin-top: 6px; }
    .metric span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .highlights {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .card {
      border-radius: 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .card h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .card p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer-links { margin-top: 18px; }
    @media (max-width: 840px) {
      .hero, .highlights, .nav { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="nav">
      <div>
        <div class="brand">s-sleeve hybrid care platform</div>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Open live dashboard</a>
        <a href="/server/operations">Operations</a>
        <a href="/server/reports">Reports</a>
        <a href="/server/variables">Variables</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hero">
      <article class="panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Server-rendered launch surface</p>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p class="subtitle"><%= subtitle %></p>
        <%- heroMarkup %>
        <div class="cta-row" style="margin-top: 20px;">
          <a class="primary" href="/">Jump into the Angular dashboard</a>
          <a href="/server/reports">Open morning reporting</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <aside class="panel status-card">
        <div class="status-pill">
          <span class="status-dot"></span>
          <span><%= status %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span>Care pathways</span>
            <strong>12</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span>Active monitors</span>
            <strong>47</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span>Review queue</span>
            <strong>5</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span>Pending kits</span>
            <strong>7</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <% if (showHighlights) { %>
    <section class="highlights">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Clinician handoff</h2>
        <p>Use the server side hub to stage briefings, print-ready summaries, and stable low-JS entry pages for outreach teams.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Angular handoff</h2>
        <p>The live telemetry dashboard remains the rich client surface for motion playback, variables tuning, and observable-driven interactions.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Compiler handoff</h2>
        <p>This page is compiled from EJS into C route handlers alongside the existing Angular-like frontend pipeline.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
    <% } %>

    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/server/welcome.txt">Plain text health route</a>
      <a href="/server/api/launch">POST launch endpoint</a>
      <a href="/server/variables">Printable variables view</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
